text: Injra railway station () is located in union council of Tarap. It has a police station. Injra is located in Jand Tehsil of District Attock, Punjab, Pakistan. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Attock District Category:Railway stations on Kotri–Attock Railway Line (ML 2)
